articles.author: Sarah Carter, Adam Duxter
articles.title: Elephant attack leaves American woman dead in Zambia's Kafue National Park - CBS News
articles.description: A safari tour operator in Zambia says an American woman was killed by an elephant because their ranger couldn't move the vehicle "out of harm's way quick enough."
articles.content: Johannesburg — An elephant attack that left an American woman dead in Zambia was captured in harrowing cellphone video over the weekend. The clip, shot by tourists in Zambia's Kafue National Park, be… [+1875 chars]
